 * group:hero => 首屏内容
 * hero.display => 显示首屏:select:yes|yes,no
 * hero.title => 首屏标题:text:Boot-To-Show Speed Lane
 * hero.subtitle => 首屏副标题:textarea:From blind opening to final show, this Teen Patti layout keeps route choice, pot status, and action timing clear on every screen.
